<br>
If you created a character *on* Stormhammer, and then quit legends, you have your choice of which server you want to go to, as is the case with my BST, Dugal.  No reason for me to go anywhere but my home server though =)<br>
<br>
Also, your characters that move back are subject to removal of items.  Yes, if you go to stormhammer from one of the newer servers that say, don't have manastones on them at *all*...buy a manastone, and then try to transfer that character with stone back to your old server, they'll strip the item.  This is to keep items that have been removed from the game for balance reasons from getting introduced into &quot;pristine environments&quot;.<br>
<br>
Side note, you don't have to quit legends service to get characters moved.  I'm maintaining my legends account, keeping my lvl 60 over on stormhammer, just simply moving my BST back to my home server so I can group with people =)<br>
